# Fastify Best Practices

- Use schema validation for routes to improve performance and security
- Implement proper error handling with custom error handlers
- Utilize Fastify's plugin system for modular code organization
- Configure appropriate logging with pino for production environments
- Use reply decorators for consistent response formatting